column5: Any information as to quality and quantity of Pike/Walleye and trout fishing on Whitefish Lake, I know there a lot of cottages and several Lodges around as this is a drive to lake. What is the fishing like in September/October?
Does anyone have any experience or insight of this lake? Might be a future destination.
I had a pretty great trip there a couple springs ago:https://www.canadafishingguide.net/a...ir-dale-lodge/
